                "html": "The practice of conjuring and binding shining children to serve as guardians of important locations was a popular one in Thassilon. Even today, thousands of years after this empire\u2019s fall, adventurers can still encounter shining children in ancient ruins, guarding treasures and forgotten lore from the distant past."
